  "title": "Locum/Flexi Healthcare Assistant! #HYNT",
  "description": "<p>We are seeking contract Healthcare Assistants to be outsourced to various healthcare organizations across Singapore!</p><p><strong>Job Description:</strong>    </p><ul><li>Prepare patients for procedures, ensuring they are well-informed and at ease</li><li>Maintain infection control by sterilizing instruments and setting up procedure trays</li><li>Assist healthcare staff during procedures and respond promptly in emergencies</li><li>Provide empathetic and attentive care to create a supportive patient experience</li><li>Monitor and support patients throughout their clinic visit</li><li>Handle administrative tasks such as appointment scheduling and medical record updates</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Strong interpersonal and communication skills.</li><li>Experience is required</li></ul><p><strong>How to Apply:</strong></p><p>Please send your resume to rehealth@recruitexpress.com.sg.</p><p>We regret to inform you that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p>Chloe Impens| Outsourcing Team<br />EA License Number: 99C4599<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd | Company Reg. No. 199601303W</p>",
